Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐乃桐乃  你爸昨天在參觀你工作的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.63,0:00:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍照的時候被當做可疑人物啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要你多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一著急  就說「不…不是  這是我女兒」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要學我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  爸爸你啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:03:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們社長看上了加奈子  要她下次去面試
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了的話  可能會進事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是偶像的第一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次的骯髒的工作體驗一下也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  桐乃等級的我大概很快就追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  加奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子肯定會合格的  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我家那個妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「早上好」啊「Thankyou」啊「你的份」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是桐乃  是長著桐乃臉的什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意  桐乃一定也開始想要直率地感謝小京的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  總覺得有什麼不對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你「呃」什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好哥哥  上次承蒙你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢  桐乃也非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小京的熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是桐乃的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  我是新垣綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是田村麻奈實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  小京的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有特別奇怪的地方啊  和平常一樣的桐乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼的話我也會發覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊  問了些奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實提出搞活動的是在下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐乃乃氏也很贊同才做準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得並沒有特別勉強的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是我想多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為京介氏太在意桐乃乃氏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你了  我要掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nyoron
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}(註：小涼宮鶴屋前輩的口頭必備萌音）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能來下我的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像變乾淨了呢  這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微整理了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要說的話是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上次說的最後的探討人生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說也算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  說說看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你幫我買工口遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我絕對沒有偷哥哥的短褲哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個「3D定製妹妹」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是「哥褲」和「定製妹」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼略稱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩部我想讓你深夜排隊幫我買
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是最後的探討人生嗎  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要拜託我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是因為這種事哪怕快一秒做也是好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照預定傍晚睡上一覺  等你把遊戲買回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備一直玩到早上  通完一條線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做到這種地步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要啊  當然要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊  那間店不是在秋葉原嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算晚上12點去買回到家也要過1點了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被老爸發現…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊我會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他們的動向我會用電話聯繫你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何我都想快點玩到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好  這是最後了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦  我去買就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉赤城  今晚就當我住在你家行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和田村好好玩哦  拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像誤會了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全部都是桐乃的同類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加深夜發售的客人  請在這裡排隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎著那個到這裡來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  最末尾是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤…赤城？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是拜託你就當今晚我住在你家的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會來買工口遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面有很深的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  我還以為你和田村去了什麼地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會來買工口遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面有很深的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來彼此都有苦衷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就當我們根本沒有在這裡見過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你都沒有去秋葉原的深夜發售
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有排隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒有買什麼工口遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情是不求回報的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預定了「搞基部」的客人  請到這裡排隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你你…那個就是所謂的純搞基遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂  你誤會大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  看著我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是基
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實那是純搞基遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那我妹妹拜託我來買的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:10:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹不還是初中生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個世界會有讓哥哥去買工口遊戲的初中生妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼認同了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上有太多無法用常識來解釋的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷疑你真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你能理解就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹玩基情遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家妹妹就是所謂的腐女子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是婦人的婦  而是腐臭的腐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上幻想男人間的戀愛或親密關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷地享受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是喜歡基啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡了  熱愛著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要拍手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道  我已經明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我了去那邊的隊伍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了  開始發售了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聽從工作人員的引導購買商品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼從前面的人開始每次十人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我「短褲」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要「哥哥的短褲」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是收銀台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一趟電車還趕得上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我你腦袋的尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是說過嗎  要給你做一個貓耳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快告訴我你那又大又圓的腦袋的尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊  這種事用郵件問不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚伺服器維修上不了線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以打算錄在電話留言裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然明天也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但莫名地想要今晚問你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還醒著太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  你把我錯當誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了  也真虧哥哥會容忍你的旁若無人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了  話說你能不能不要那麼叫他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你這麼一叫他就一副扭捏的樣子真是噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒沒看出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關係  到時稱呼就會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶打開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上得出去一次才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上學也別遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩嗎  很久沒一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…別靠太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:14:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法呀  不這樣我就看不到畫面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安裝完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我才沒有偷哥哥的內褲哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次雖然女主角只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是相對卻有很多路線
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次通關都會增加選項  結局也會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這也是經常有的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有潛入一樣的迷你遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡得到的道具可以用來立flag
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼結局  也太悲傷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  他們又不是生離死別
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打打電話不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見的時候見不到很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己換位思考一下試試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想的話的確是個寂寞的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得回收一下分歧路線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達成一個結局了  已經可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探討人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說那是最後的探討人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才去買工口遊戲的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼  說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  從那以後都過了9個月了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得那時的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那個時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有因為害羞沒讓你看的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有好好保密  也沒有看不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還幫了我那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是比動畫和工口遊戲更糟糕的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很害羞  還是讓你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像的要普通嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹的東西不可能這麼普通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是那個很糟糕  相冊很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不知道那裡面放了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  這本相冊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:53.52,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(550,137)\fad(0,600)} 不看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:53.52,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(55,137)\fad(0,600)} 看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  給我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到這個地步  我做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是蒙在鼓裡才更讓人精神上不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿來吧  給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出來的可是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  我改變主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒你事了  快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差遣別人一整晚  怎麼這個態度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:35.52,SPEC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(40,250)\fad(0,200)}東京/成田\N↓\N洛杉磯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去美國嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊接受田徑訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在升高中前不會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天合宿的時候  被那邊的教練看上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這是次不錯的機會就接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…為什麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是突然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這半年來都在通過工作和小說的錢籌備費用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也和父親和母親說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下天亮去機場了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就瞞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我不在了  和你有關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會現在說叫我不要去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備也全部做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也覺得我煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得你很煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如你所說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田徑  美國
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯的機會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有阻止你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事和我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說我也會去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就去  立刻就去  給我去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死  去死  去死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（留住法奈）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「說聲『不要走』呀  哥哥」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「哥哥要留住我的話  我哪裡都不去了」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「夢想在哪裡都能實現  但哥哥只在這裡」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「謝謝你  哥哥」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「今後也要一直在一起哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就清靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  飯還夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐乃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩人  讓開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  爸爸媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛機是幾點來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早飯吃了再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去美國了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去了  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我會去各處道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上我會說明的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.97,0:22:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我到是不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.64,0:22:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國又遠  你也還只是中學生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老是說去吧去吧的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然覺得很不爽  掃興了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和你沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.03,0:22:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過英語也還需要學習一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有梅露露的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和綾瀨她們分開也會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.77,0:22:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進了高中再編入也比較方便
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且錢也能適當返還一些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:23:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸媽媽…那些傢伙也會寂寞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊要買工口遊戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始就幹嘛笑嘻嘻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超噁心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  笨～蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.73,0:23:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小京早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天似乎心情很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是  我的妹妹
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.68,0:25:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.54,0:25:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.77,0:25:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.61,0:25:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事需要…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.19,0:25:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探討人生
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.45,0:25:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.38,0:27:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.05,0:27:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹的探討人生不可能就這麼結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.65,0:27:17.63,NEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(110,60)\fs32\fsp-3}我妹妹的探討人生不可能就這麽結束了
